    352  f17f							; in GRP1's old latch and bleeds into the score's top row next frame, where
    353  f17f							; VDELP1=1 displays it. (The old 8-row loop cleared both latches by drawing
    354  f17f							; its two blank bottom rows; this doubled loop must do it explicitly.)
